desc:
The holiday season is kicking off, and it's a wonderful time to celebrate!?Join DE-CIX New York to toast our customers, partners and friends. We have much to celebrate - a wonderful year of growth, success and the milestone of 100 networks peering at our exchange. We look forward to seeing you there.
